x equals 5 over the square root of x minus 1.

22
00:01:54.066 --> 00:01:58.993
First. the denominator cannot be zero. so x cannot be

23
00:01:59.093 --> 00:02:04.210
1. Second. the expression under the square root must be

24
00:02:04.310 --> 00:02:07.814
